Sure, here are some example sentences that use the Serbian word "bacim" in different forms and positions:

1. *Bacim* loptu u koš. (I throw the ball into the basket.)
2. Kad se sretnemo, *bacimo* zajedno. (When we meet, we'll throw together.)
3. *Bacio* sam smeće u kontejner. (I threw the garbage in the bin.)
4. Sutra ću *baciti* pogled na taj problem. (Tomorrow I will take a look at that problem.)
5. Kada *baciš* kamenčić u vodu, napravi se krug. (When you throw a stone in the water, a circle is formed.)
6. *Bacite* novčić da odlučimo ko će prvi birati. (Flip a coin to decide who will choose first.)
7. Čim *bacim* pogled na nju, znam da će sve biti u redu. (As soon as I lay my eyes on her, I know everything will be fine.)
8. Nemoj *bacati* hranu, mnogi ljudi nemaju šta da jedu. (Don't throw away food, many people have nothing to eat.)

I hope this helps! Let me know if you have any other questions.